// complexity was previously scored as "excellent" (0.95) for languages that
// can't actually measure complexity (TierGeneric). With the fix, complexity=0
// on an unsupported language must not produce a maintainability dimension
// set to 0.95.
func TestScore_UnmeasuredComplexity_NotScored(t *testing.T) {
